OL,5, A professor has lost a university role 
OL,6, after he described the use of the Welsh
OL,7, language on road signs as "potentially 
OL,8, dangerous".                            
OL,10,FNigel Hunt, a visiting psychology      
OL,11,Fprofessor at Wrexham University posted 
OL,12,Fthe comments on social media.          
OL,14,FHe said he got a letter from the       
OL,15,Funiversity's vice chancellor,          
OL,16,Fdismissing him from the honorary       
OL,17,Fposition.                              
OL,19,FThe university confirmed Prof Hunt no  
OL,20,Flonger worked there.                   
